Question:- what is the main problem with inheritance that i can explain in interview
ğŸ”¥ Main Problems with Inheritance
            Tight Coupling â€“ Subclasses depend heavily on the base class.
            Fragile Base Class â€“ Changes in the base class can break subclasses.
            Inflexibility â€“ Hard to change or reuse part of the inherited behavior.
            Single Inheritance Limitation â€“ Can't inherit from multiple classes.
            Hierarchy Overgrowth â€“ Leads to deep, complex class hierarchies.
